<p>
If you&#39;ve been using Emacs for a while, I bet you must have encountered the annoying problem that your Emacs window layout gets messed up after some operations, such as looking for a help (e.g. <code class="verbatim">C-h k</code>), or checking things in the magit status buffer.</p>
